    "description": "<i>感受狼群的恐怖吧。它们冷酷，它们嗜血 – 为了生存，它们勇往直前从不退缩…</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/vikings_logo4.gif.png?t=1490374637\" /></span><br><br>诸神的黄昏－－传说当最严酷的寒冬降临时，巨人族将向阿斯加德（注：北欧神话中的神界）诸神复仇。世界将走向毁灭，米德加德（注：北欧神话中的人界）命悬一线。然而，当冰火两族巨人集结军队之时，他们遭到了有“米德加德群狼”之称的沃尔松格部落的抵抗。该部落村庄遭到毁灭后，这群流离失所的维京战士并未屈服，他们决心要掌控自己的命运，同时以拯救世界为己任。作为部落酋长，你必须率领族群与芬布尔之冬中的各种凶猛生物战斗，将米德加德从灭亡的边缘中拯救。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/vikings_art-02.jpg?t=1490374637\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/horizontal4.png?t=1490374637\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >北欧神话与奇幻故事相结合</h2><strong>化身骁勇善战的维京战士，深入米德加德之境，转战冰雪国度尼福尔海姆和火巨人王国巴尔海姆。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/horizontal4.png?t=1490374637\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >严酷的芬布尔之冬</h2><strong>忍受致命严寒，千万别在这样的风雪中待太久，小心被大自然吞噬。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/horizontal4.png?t=1490374637\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >献祭诸神</h2><strong>从杀死的敌人身上收集鲜血，通过祭坛献给诸神，提升自身力量。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/horizontal4.png?t=1490374637\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >狂战士之怒</h2><strong>开启狂怒模式浴血奋战，借助怒火之力碾压敌人。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/horizontal4.png?t=1490374637\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗之道</h2><strong>剑、弓、法杖等多中武器可供选择，研习每一类武器，领会其中奥义。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/horizontal4.png?t=1490374637\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >诸神之力</h2><strong>装备神器，如索尔或洛基的护身符，让诸神之力成为你的力量。完成诸神的试炼来提升技能，并获取丰厚的奖励。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/horizontal4.png?t=1490374637\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >团队协作</h2><strong>叫上朋友一同探索米德加德海岸，在双人协作模式中开启史诗之旅。根据自身水平，从四种难度中选择挑战。还可开启残酷的硬核模式，敢来一战否？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612420/extras/vikings_art-01.jpg?t=1490374637\" /></span>",
